    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## AI as a Mathematician\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to solve a math problem.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Find the section in your **Unit Guide** labeled \"Solving a math problem\". \r\n2. Choose one of the math problems below and rank how well you think a human would do.\r\n3. **Write** a prompt asking AI Chat to solve that problem or something similar.\r\n4. Press **Send**.\r\n5. Then read **AI Chat's response**. \r\n6. Rank how well AI did and complete the table in your **Unit Guide**.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nChoose one of the math problems below. Click to expand:\r\n\r\n::: details [**Basic Calculation**] \r\n>What is 289 × 42? Show your work step by step.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Word Problem**]\r\n>If a train leaves Chicago at 3:00 PM traveling 60 mph and another train leaves New York at 4:00 PM traveling 80 mph, when will they meet?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Logic-Based Math Problem**]\r\n>A farmer has 17 sheep. All but 9 run away. How many are left?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Creative Math Question**]\r\n>Can you tell me the largest number less than 100 that is both a perfect square and a perfect cube?\r\n:::\r\n",
